#include <iostream>
#include <stdio.h>
using namespace std;
int main() {
	int t;	
	cin>>t;
	while(t--){
		int K,L,M,N; 
		fscanf(stdin,"%d %d %d %d",&K,&L,&M,&N);
		int P,Q,R,S; 
		fscanf(stdin,"%d %d %d %d",&P,&Q,&R,&S);

		int x1,y1,x2,y2;
		x1 = max(K,P);
		y1= max(L,Q);
		x2 = min(M,R);
		y2 = min(N,S);

		if (x1>=x2 || y1>=y2) 
			cout<<"No Overlap";
		
		else 
			cout<<x1<<" "<<y1<<" "<<x2<<" "<<y2<<endl;
		
	}
}
